<template>
    <v-row align="center" justify="center">
        <v-card height="300" width="250">
            <v-row justify="center">
                <v-btn
                        color="success"
                        class="mt-12"
                        @click="overlay = !overlay"
                >
                    Show Overlay
                </v-btn>

                <v-overlay
                        :absolute="absolute"
                        :value="overlay"
                >
                    <v-btn
                            color="success"
                            @click="overlay = false"
                    >
                        Hide Overlay
                    </v-btn>
                </v-overlay>
            </v-row>
        </v-card>
    </v-row>
</template>

<script>
    export default {
        name: "SinginPage",

        methods: {

            data: () => ({
                absolute: true,
                overlay: false,
            }),
        },

    }
</script>

<style scoped>

</style>
